<text id="02-output-contract" title="Asset Harvest Checklist Output Contract" version="1.0.0" est_tokens="800" depth="essential">
  <summary>Pins the starter-kit layout, harvest-log shape, and per-asset metadata schema.</summary>

  <section title="Required starter-kit layout">
    <list>
      <item><code>lib/</code> — utility modules with SPDX headers</item>
      <item><code>copy/</code> — landing page variants, FAQ, onboarding emails</item>
      <item><code>ui/</code> — reusable components (framework-tagged subfolders)</item>
      <item><code>illustrations/</code> — owned visual assets (SVG, Lottie, generated)</item>
      <item><code>schema/</code> — DB migrations, OpenAPI specs, JSON schemas</item>
      <item><code>deploy/</code> — deploy scripts, dockerfiles, CI configs</item>
      <item><code>infra/</code> — Terraform / k8s / secret patterns</item>
      <item><code>LICENSE</code> — root SPDX declaration</item>
      <item><code>harvest-log.md</code> — chronological log</item>
    </list>
    <reference path="templates/starter-kit-layout.md">Detailed conventions per folder.</reference>
  </section>

  <section title="Harvest-log required fields">
    <list>
      <item><code>sunset_date_utc</code></item>
      <item><code>source_product</code> (name + repo URL if any)</item>
      <item><code>harvest_started_utc</code> + <code>harvest_completed_utc</code></item>
      <item><code>sections</code>: per-section list of extractions (S1..S7)</item>
      <item><code>extractions[].source</code> (repo-relative path in dead product)</item>
      <item><code>extractions[].destination</code> (path in starter-kit)</item>
      <item><code>extractions[].generalisation</code>: enum {verbatim, parameterised, rewritten}</item>
      <item><code>extractions[].license</code>: SPDX identifier</item>
      <item><code>extractions[].lesson</code>: 1-2 sentences with concrete experience</item>
    </list>
    <reference path="templates/harvest-log.md">Harvest log template.</reference>
  </section>

  <section title="Per-asset metadata schema">
    <list>
      <item><code>asset_id</code> (stable id within starter-kit)</item>
      <item><code>origin_product</code> (name)</item>
      <item><code>origin_commit</code> (SHA from dead product if recoverable)</item>
      <item><code>license</code> (SPDX)</item>
      <item><code>version</code> (semver, starts at 0.1.0)</item>
      <item><code>generalisation_level</code> (enum)</item>
      <item><code>last_updated_utc</code></item>
    </list>
    <reference path="templates/asset-metadata.json">Per-asset metadata schema.</reference>
  </section>

  <section title="Forbidden patterns">
    <antipattern>
      <description>Harvested file without SPDX header.</description>
      <reason>r2 violation. License declaration is required per file.</reason>
    </antipattern>
    <antipattern>
      <description>Extraction source path matches a client-engagement repo or contains client / customer name.</description>
      <reason>r3 violation. Client code is out.</reason>
    </antipattern>
    <antipattern>
      <description>Log entry without `lesson` field.</description>
      <reason>r5 violation. Lessons are what compound; without them the starter kit is just code.</reason>
    </antipattern>
    <antipattern>
      <description>Harvest started &gt; 14 days after sunset date.</description>
      <reason>r1 violation. Context has decayed.</reason>
    </antipattern>
  </section>

  <section title="Self-check checklist">
    <list>
      <item>Every extraction has source + destination + generalisation + license + lesson.</item>
      <item>SPDX header present in every harvested file.</item>
      <item>No client-repo path appears in `source`.</item>
      <item>Schema (S1) + deploy (S2) sections harvested first if applicable.</item>
      <item>Starter-kit LICENSE declared at root.</item>
    </list>
  </section>
</text>
